messages.message: For sonarcube failures, what do they mean by "coverage"? It seems like sonarcube is flagging cypress tests as uncovered code (https://sonar.scan.instabase.com/component_measures?id=instabase.master&metric=new_lines_to_cover&pullRequest=66813&view=list&selected=instabase.master%3Awebserver%2Fshared%2Fsrc%2Fjs%2Fwebpacked%2Fapps%2Fsrc%2Faihub%2F__e2e__%2FDeployments%2Fedit-deployment.spec.ts)
We just saw one of these on Udit's PR! That's a good call out that it's flagging Cypress code. Fortunately the checks aren't blocking yet...
